OL,3,CGovernment announces review into the
OL,4,Cpension age - what does it mean for
OL,5,Cyou?
OL,7,FThe Work and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,8,FKendall has announced the a review
OL,9,Finto the age you will be able to
OL,10,Fretire.
OL,12,FThe last time a review was conducted
OL,13,Fit resulted in the state pension age
OL,14,Fbeing increased to 67, an increase
OL,15,Fcoming in to effect between 2026 and
OL,16,F2028.
OL,18,FThe previous government had already
OL,19,Fpromised a review in the first two
OL,20,Fyears of this parliament into whether
OL,21,Fthis should be increased further to 68.
