OL,3,CGovernment announces review into the
OL,4,Cpension age - what does it mean for
OL,5,Cyou?
OL,7,FIn its previous incarnation under the
OL,8,FBlair government it saw the
OL,9,Fintroduction of automatic enrollment
OL,10,Finto pension schemes for eligible
OL,11,Findividuals, a move that increased the
OL,12,Fnumber of employees saving to 88%, up
OL,13,Ffrom 2012's 55%.
OL,15,FThis is a developing story, more to
OL,16,Ffollow.
